description: Welcome to this beautiful, sunlit 2-bedroom penthouse condo located in desirable City Point with incredible view of Boston Harbor and the surrounding city. Recently updated, this unit has a spacious feel to the living, dining, bedrooms and generous kitchen with direct access to private rooftop deck. New heat/ac condenser (2024); mini-splits (2020-23), updated bathroom (2022), dishwasher, new disposal (2019), ample kitchen cabinets, stainless appliances and a breakfast bar, along with in-unit laundry, hardwood floors throughout and additional storage in basement complete this home. Pet-friendly and only 1 block to the Park as well as major bus lines 5,7,9,10,11. Short distance to M Street Beach, grocery store etc. The angled street parking is an absolute bonus if you have a car. Other upgrades include: new building door lock system, common stairs painted/re-carpeted (since 2019); replaced screens (2019); replaced back door, threshold, painted all walls and new washer/dryer (2023)
